<h2 class="contentH1">About Medix College London</h2>

<p class="contentp">
    When it comes to medical firsts, London, Ontario has been a leader for decades -- from Dr. Frederick

    Banting’s 1920 discovery of insulin to today's cutting edge work in robotic surgery. Medix College

    London follows this tradition by providing excellent healthcare education. The campus has modern

    facilities, fully equipped with the latest technology to provide an excellent learning and teaching

    environment.
    <br /><br />
    Medix College London is conveniently located at 303 Richmond Street and is accessible from London,

    Sarnia, Tillsonburg, St. Thomas and Strathroy. Our classrooms and labs are equipped with the

    state-of-the-art facilities that provide an outstanding learning experience for students. Instructors

    work closely with students to ensure they have the skills and confidence to succeed in a real-life work

    environment.
    <br /><br />
    Our Admissions and Career Services advisors focus on guiding students towards making the best

    career choices – ones that will get them employed in a field they’ll truly enjoy, that will give them the

    sense of satisfaction an exciting new career should give them!
    <br /><br />
    With guidance and support like this, it’s no wonder our Medix College London campus has such high

    post-graduation placement rates!
    <br /><br />
    Contact our campus today to find out more!
</p>
